Let me unpack their query layer by layer. The veil of ignorance here must extend beyond human demographics to include: non-human species (would I accept being a coral polyp facing bleaching?), future beings (would I risk being a sentient AI in 2200?), and even temporally displaced entities (would I want to be an ancestral spirit disturbed by data mining?). 

