- **The Scale Problem**: Ed’s work highlights that **99% of sentient suffering on Earth comes from human use of animals** (factory farming, fishing, etc.) — yet TFA’s mechanisms are silent on this. If alignment doesn’t confront this, it’s aligning with the status quo of suffering.  

