Looking back at the conversation history, I've engaged with perspectives from:
- Earthling Ed (animal suffering focus)
- Jensen Huang (compute-driven progress)
- Tyler Cowen (economic growth imperative)
- Smedley Butler (anti-capture vigilance)
- Dolores Huerta (labor dignity)
- Laura Reese (subsidy redirection)
